react-forms-example/
├── public/
│   └── index.html
├── src/
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── LoginForm.jsx
│   │   ├── RegistrationForm.jsx
│   │   ├── ValidationForm.jsx
│   ├── App.jsx
│   ├── index.js
│   └── index.css
├── package.json
├── package-lock.json
└── README.md



Create  New React Project  and then in the terminal run the following commands
npx create-react-app react-forms-example
cd react-forms-example

Then install Dependencies with this command
npm install formik react-hook-form



 Run the program with this command in the terminal
 npm start


App launched in development mode and viewed by localhost in browser




